## Parallel Execution Opportunities

### Pattern 1: Main Task + Documentation
```
Task completes
  ├─> Continue with next interaction
  └─> [PARALLEL] @keeper: Update docs
```

### Pattern 2: Independent Validations
```
Multiple checks needed
  ├─> @worker instance 1: Check A
  ├─> @worker instance 2: Check B
  └─> @worker instance 3: Check C
```

